\b
\li1 
\v 8 Now these are the names of the sons of Israel (Jacob and his descendants) who went to Egypt: Reuben, Jacob’s firstborn.
\b
\li1 
\v 9 The sons of Reuben: Hanoch, Pallu, Hezron, and Carmi.
\b
\li1 
\v 10 The sons of Simeon: Jemuel,\f + \fr 46:10 \ft Jemuel is another name for Nemuel; see Numbers 26:12.\f* Jamin, Ohad, Jachin, Zohar,\f + \fr 46:10 \ft Zohar is a variant of Zerah; see Numbers 26:13 and 1 Chronicles 4:24.\f* and Shaul the son of a Canaanite woman.
