\b
\li1 
\v 15 These are the sons of Leah born to Jacob in Paddan-aram,\f + \fr 46:15 \ft That is, northwest Mesopotamia\f* in addition to his daughter Dinah. The total number of sons and daughters was thirty-three.
\s2 The Children of Zilpah
\b
\li1 
