\s2 The Children of Rachel
\b
\li1 
\v 19 The sons of Jacob’s wife Rachel: Joseph and Benjamin.
\b
\li1 
\v 20 Manasseh and Ephraim were born to Joseph in the land of Egypt by Asenath daughter of Potiphera, priest of On.\f + \fr 46:20 \ft That is, Heliopolis, as in LXX\f*
\b
\li1 
